\ip \bd ?Nat…®gi…ôn t…ôhro lanu nian t…ôm…ôtei?\bd* Jon in i…ôt…ômi asoli k…ôti r…ôha nim…ôfaki, k…ôni n…ôt…ômimi r…ôfin r…ôha nim…ôfaki kaut…®siai in. In tolkeikei m…ôm…ô n…ôt…ômimi r…ôfin okot…ôhrun vivi r…ôhan n…ôg…ôtuni…ôn, k…ôni nian n…ôg…ôtuni…ôn eiu…ô t…ôtan, m…ôt…ôu n…ôt…ômimi kot…ôhrun naht…®p…ôs…®gi…ôn e n…ôghati…ôn eiu…ô m…®n e n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha Jon e nau…ôu…ô u.
