\v 1 \fig N…ôua krep|alt="Grapevine" src="lb00107b.tif" size="span" loc="Jhn 15:1-8" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="Jon 15:1-8"\fig*K…ôni Iesu t…ôni m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôu u,\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Jon 6:35\f* i…ôu i…ôk…ôhmen e n…ôuk…ôt…® n…®gi p…ôhri…ôn. K…ôni r…ôhak Tat…ô in t…ôhmen e i…ôt…ômimi i…ôt…ôm t…ôt…ôtahl…®n n…®gi u.\f + \fr 15:1 \ft Aes 5:1-7\f*
