\v 17 I…ôt…ôf…®n…ô n…ôghati…ôn k…ôti k…ôm t…ômah in tol lanu. It…ômah on…ôkot…ôkeikei motolkeikei it…ômah m…®n.‚Äù\f + \fr 15:17 \ft Jon 15:12\f*
