\v 21 Ilah okotol natimnati m…®n lan…ôha, m…ôt…ôu-inu it…ômah r…ôhak m…®n n…ôt…ômimi.\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Aes 66:5; Mat 5:10-12; 10:22; Luk 6:22-23; U…ôk 5:41; 1Pit…ô 4:14; N…ôh 2:3\f* Ilah okotol lan…ôha, m…ôt…ôu-inu ilah kot…ôruru Uhg…®n i…ôt…ôm t…ômahli=pa i…ôu.\f + \fr 15:21 \ft Jon 16:1-3\f*
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúI…ômuva k…ôni m…ôghati k…ôm lah. Tol lan…ôha n…ôua n…ôghati…ôn u, ilah k…ômoteruh …ôsas r…ôhalah noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n. M…ôt…ôu k…ômot…ôuhlin mat…ôlg…®lah ohni…ôu mot…ôp…ôh r…ôhak n…ôghati…ôn. K…ôni r…ôueiu, ko k…ôsot…ôni…ôn m…ôm…ô r…ôhalah noli…ôn t…ôrah t…®k…ô.\f + \fr 15:22 \ft Iesu t…®nuva k…ôni mol …ôpu r…ôhalah noli…ôn t…ôrah, k…ôni mol suaru o n…®t…®si…ôn ilah e t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah. M…ôt…ôu n…ôt…ômimi r…ôha n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni k…ôut…ôm…ôki m…ôm…ô inko Iesu tatol …ôpu noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n r…ôhalah. Tol lan…ôha, ilah kot…ôp…ôh in k…ôni mautoht…ôu=p…ôn napin…ôpui…ôn mapir…ôk…®s n…ôhag…ôhagi…ôn, k…ôni nati u in t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah asoli. (Jon 3:19-21; 9:39-41)\f*\f + \fr 15:22 \ft Jon 9:41; Rom 1:20; 2:1; Luk 11:31-32\f*
