\v 27 Konu it…ômah m…®n, on…ôkot…ôkeikei mot…ôhtul p…ôt…®g…ôm mot…ôni i…ôu,\f + \fr 15:27 \ft Luk 24:48; Jon 21:24; 1Jon 1:2; 4:14\f* m…ôt…ôu-inu it…ômah nautat…®g kitah min i…ôu e n…ôtu…ôuini…ôn e u…ôk r…ôhak muva m…ôt…ôuarus=pa u r…ôueiu.
