\v 10 Saimon Pit…ô t…ômat…ôl…ôs r…ôhan k…ôti nau r…ôha n…ôluag…®ni…ôn. K…ôni …ômeiko, in t…ômeuvi p…ôt…®g…ôm u…ôhai …ôm…ô r…ôhan nau, mau…ôh lan mohatuv r…ôk…®s n…®mat…ôlg…® iolu…ôk k…ôti r…ôha pris asoli ag…®n, n…®mat…ôlg…®n maru. N…ôrg…® suah k…ôha, Malk…ôs.
