\v 5 \fig N…®l…ôu…®s k…ôti tol nihl…®n-nihl…®n|alt="Briers" src="hk00122b.tif" size="span" loc="Jhn 19:5" copy="BFBS (Knowles)" ref="Jon 19:5"\fig*K…ôni Iesu t…ômiet m…®n muva ihlu…ô. In t…ôt…ôf…ôfau e k…ôf…ôfau u k…ômol e l…ôhi i…ôt…ôm tol nihl…®n-nihl…®n, t…ôhmen e k…ôf…ôfau r…ôha kig, k…ôni matuv…ôn e kot …ôf…ôm…ôh tol n…ôug…® naris, t…ôhmen e kot r…ôha kig, k…ôni Pail…ôt t…ôni=p…ôn k…ôm lah m…ôm…ô, ‚Äú!N…ôt…ômimi! !Oteh-to! Suah u inu!‚Äù
