\r (Mat 27:32-44; Mak 15:21-32; Luk 23:26-43)
\p K…ôni ilah k…ômot…ôl…ôs Iesu m…ôhuv…ôn.
\v 17 In tat…ôl…ôs n…®gi k…ôm…ôluau r…ôhan,\f + \fr 19:17 \ft Luk 14:27\f* miet matuv…ôn ik…®n k…ôti m…®n, n…ôrg…®n u, Kolkot…ô e n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôm Isrel. N…®p…ôt…®n u, ‚ÄúLouip…®l-uip…®l.‚Äù
\v 18 K…ôni ik…®n …ôha, k…ômot…ôtu-p…ôri Iesu e n…®gi k…ôm…ôluau. K…ôni k…ômotat…®g mot…ôhti=p…ôn m…®n i…ôt…ômimi mil keiu e n…®gi k…ôm…ôluau keiu m…®n, k…ôti e n…®kal…®n maru, k…ôti e n…®kal…®n m…ôu…®l, k…ôni Iesu in t…ôt…ôhkul e n…ôlug…®n e lau.
\p 
\v 19 K…ôni Pail…ôt t…ôm…ôni k…ôtei r…ôk…®s n…ôghati…ôn k…ôti, k…ôl…ôs kan k…ôhti=p…ôn e r…ôhn-kap…ô n…®gi k…ôm…ôluau. N…ôghati…ôn u t…ôt…ôni m…ôm…ô,\fig |alt="Jesus on cross" src="lb00324b.tif" size="col" loc="Jhn 19:19" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="Jon 19:19"\fig*
\pc \sc Iesu\sc*
