\v 20 K…ôni n…ôt…ôm Isrel tep…ôt, ilah kotafin n…ôghati…ôn u, m…ôt…ôu-inu ik…®n …ôha k…ômot…ôhti=p…ôn Iesu ik…®n, in iu…ôk…®r …ôm…ô o taun.\f + \fr 19:20 \ft Hip 13:12\f* K…ôni n…ôghati…ôn u, k…ôm…ôtei r…ôk…®s e n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôm Isrel, m…®ne n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôm Rom, m…®ne n…ôghati…ôn r…ôha n…ôt…ôm Kris.
